snippet.title: Magic & Mayhem 2: The Art of Magic Walkthrough Part 1
snippet.description: Part 1 of my walkthrough of the Art of Magic - a game by Mythos Games. Many gamers disliked the game because of mediocre graphics and really linear plot. However, many of my bright childhood memories are about this game. Enjoy!
